301
00:23:12,840 --> 00:23:13,680
Good night.

302
00:23:55,080 --> 00:23:55,920
Asha.

303
00:23:56,280 --> 00:23:57,600
Hello, Prakash.

304
00:23:57,680 --> 00:24:00,440
