366
00:28:15,100 --> 00:28:16,700
Yes, of course. Excuse me.

367
00:28:18,420 --> 00:28:20,300
Meet my Bhanu. Dr Prakash.

368
00:28:20,380 --> 00:28:21,860
Happy birthday. Thank you.

