00:28:27,060 --> 00:28:28,900
Excuse me.

373
00:28:30,180 --> 00:28:31,300
Why don't you dance?

374
00:28:31,700 --> 00:28:32,660
Please, Asha.

375
00:28:32,780 --> 00:28:34,980
Come on, Raju. You have no idea
how good Asha dance.

376
00:28:35,060 --> 00:28:36,660
She'll be very good
partner. Come on.

377
00:28:36,780 --> 00:28:38,100
