387
00:29:17,180 --> 00:29:18,940
I will never forget this favor.

388
00:29:20,980 --> 00:29:24,660
I promise,
you'll never see me again.

389
00:29:27,500 --> 00:29:28,780
I'll meet you.

390
00:29:30,020 --> 00:29:30,860
Really?

391
00:29:38,580 --> 00:29:41,460
