the Goddess Laxmi of our house.

531
00:39:16,000 --> 00:39:18,320
You'll stay happy only
if you'll pamper her.

532
00:39:18,960 --> 00:39:20,560
Oh, God!

533
00:39:21,360 --> 00:39:23,160
Okay dear, you sit here.
