1082
01:15:34,360 --> 01:15:36,160
Laila's messy hair.

1083
01:15:36,760 --> 01:15:38,640
Majnu's tears.

1084
01:15:39,200 --> 01:15:40,800
Farhad's heart with the work.

1085
01:15:40,880 --> 01:15:42,040
That's it.

1086
01:15:42,200 --> 01:15:45,120
