- Yes.

1102
01:16:17,720 --> 01:16:21,200
You lied to me. Get out of here.

1103
01:16:21,480 --> 01:16:23,360
Hey take him out.

1104
01:16:23,440 --> 01:16:25,680
Get him out.
- No, wait.

1105
01:16:25,760 --> 01:16:27,560
I'll go on my own.

1106
01:16:27,680 --> 01:16:28,720
Thank you.

1107
01:16:29,320 --> 01:16:32,160
