1109
01:16:33,160 --> 01:16:34,960
Get out.

1110
01:16:35,080 --> 01:16:36,120
Get out.
- Sorry.

1111
01:16:36,200 --> 01:16:37,320
You also go.

1112
01:16:37,400 --> 01:16:38,240
Go after him.

1113
01:16:38,700 --> 01:16:43,100
