1233
01:23:51,600 --> 01:23:53,800
Someone else will bring
love into your life.

1234
01:23:54,720 --> 01:23:56,480
And your life will be full of joy.

1235
01:23:57,640 --> 01:23:59,760
And you'll start loving your life.

1236
01:24:00,360 --> 01:24:02,440
