1259
01:25:13,520 --> 01:25:15,920
I know Naedimalli Raga.

1260
01:25:16,120 --> 01:25:18,680
I know Haritalmattum Godimaharaj.

1261
01:25:19,120 --> 01:25:20,600
You have knowledge about
great ragas. - Yes.

1262
01:25:20,720 --> 01:25:23,720
