- Yes.

1283
01:26:23,040 --> 01:26:23,840
You have no idea...

1284
01:26:23,920 --> 01:26:25,680
this man is a fraud.

1285
01:26:25,920 --> 01:26:27,560
He only scams.

1286
01:26:27,880 --> 01:26:30,320
